{"lemma":"نِكَتُ","slug":"نِكَتُ","root":"ن.ك.ت","root_slug":"ن-ك-ت","root_link":"/words/roots/ن-ك-ت","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n40462","n40465"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%86%D9%90%D9%83%D9%8E%D8%AA%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"point, dot, tittle, spot"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"joke, anecdote, witticism"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"conceit (artificial equivocal answer)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"odd person"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"merry-andrew, clown, buffoon"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n40462","headword_ar":"نَكَتَ","root":"nkt","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nakotN","text_ar":"نَكْتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nakata AlA^aroDa","text_ar":"نَكَتَ الاَرْضَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biqaDiybK","text_ar":"بِقَضِيبٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [&c.,] TA.)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He struck the ground with a stick,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with his finger,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so that it made a mark,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"marks, upon it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with its extremity;"},{"kind":"text","text":"an action of one reflecting, or meditating, and anxious. (TA.) [Thus our Saviour seems to have done in the case of the woman taken in adultery: see S. John viii. 6 and 8.] ―         -b2-  Also,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He struck the ground"},{"kind":"text","text":"with pebbles. (TA.) ―         -b3-  Hence, (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He reflected,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"meditated, and talked to himself"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA, from a trad.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nakata","text_ar":"نَكَتَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nakotN","text_ar":"نَكْتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a horse) bounded ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nabaA","text_ar":"نَبَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", S, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from the ground,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in running."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nakatahu","text_ar":"نَكَتَهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He threw it down upon the ground."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nakata kitaAbatahu","text_ar":"نَكَتَ كِتَابَتَهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He scattered the contents of his quiver."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nkb","text_ar":"نكب"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaEanahu fanakatahN","text_ar":"طَعَنَهُ فَنَكَتَهٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He thrust him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pierced him, and threw him down upon his head."},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, S, K. *) ―         -b8-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nukita","text_ar":"نُكِتَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a cooked bone, containing marrow,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was struck with the edge of a cake of bread,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with some other thing, to cause the marrow to fall out."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nukita AlEaZomu","text_ar":"نُكِتَ العَظْمُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The marrow to the bone was taken out,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"extracted."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Aboo-'Ameythel.) Mentioned in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bqt","text_ar":"بقت"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v. (TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nakata fiY kalAamihi","text_ar":"نَكَتَ فِى كَلاَمِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY qawolahi","text_ar":"فِى قَوْلَهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [aor,"},{"kind":"text","text":"inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nakotN","text_ar":"نَكْتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"? (in the TA, the verb is written without the syll. points, but the form commonly known in the present day, and occurring in many late works, is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nk~t","text_ar":"نكّت","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nanokiytN","text_ar":"نَنْكِيتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made use of nice,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"subtile, sayings, expressions, such as are termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nukat","text_ar":"نُكَت"},{"kind":"text","text":", pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nukotap","text_ar":"نُكْتَة"},{"kind":"text","text":")] (A.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nakatu fiY AlEilomi bimuwaAfqahi fulaAnK A^awo muxaAlafapi","text_ar":"نَكَتُ فِى العِلْمِ بِمُوَافقَهِ فُلَانٍ اَوْ مُخَالَفَةِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAni","text_ar":"فُلَانِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He alluded"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$aAra","text_ar":"اَشَارَ"},{"kind":"text","text":") ("},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with respect to science, to the agreement of such a one,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the disagreement of such a one"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (L)"}],"source_refs":["S","M","K","L"]},{"entry_id":"n40465","headword_ar":"نَكْتٌ","root":"nkt","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nukoyapN","text_ar":"نُكْيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}